## 📸 Preview

> Dark stadium-night theme with live scoreboard, ball history, 2-innings support, and target chasing.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎯 **Ball-by-ball scoring** — 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 6 runs + Wide, No Ball, Wicket
- 📊 **Live scoreboard** — Runs, Wickets, Overs, Run Rate, Extras updated instantly
- 🔄 **2-Innings support** — Complete 1st innings, then start 2nd with a target to chase
- 🎯 **Target chasing** — Live "runs needed", "balls left", and Required Run Rate (RRR)
- 🏆 **Match result** — Auto-detects win by runs, win by wickets, or tie
- ↩️ **Undo last ball** — Remove the last recorded delivery at any time
- 📜 **Ball history** — Grouped by over, shown in reverse with colour-coded chips
- 💾 **LocalStorage persistence** — Full match state restored on page reload
- 📱 **Responsive** — Works on desktop and mobile

