## 🧠 Data Structure

Match object stored in `localStorage` under key `gullyMatch`:

```json
{
  "totalOvers": 6,
  "currentInnings": 1,
  "innings1": {
    "balls": [
      { "type": "run", "value": 1 },
      { "type": "run", "value": 4 },
      { "type": "wide" },
      { "type": "wicket" }
    ]
  },
  "innings2": null
}
```

Ball types: `run` · `wicket` · `wide` · `noball`

